lines.text: Police say the body was found early this morning by a wildlife photographer in a mangrove swamp off Key Biscayne. The victim's clothes were in disarray, and police believe she may have been the victim of an assault. This is possibly the third rape/murder in as many weeks. However, police are not willing to say the murders are connected.
It's like putting your shoes on without looking.
Yeah well, a guy changing his clothes in the garage before he goes up to his apartment doesn't.
